keel.Algorithms.Fuzzy_Rule_Learning.Shared.Fuzzy

Class FuzzyInterval

  • java.lang.Object
    • keel.Algorithms.Fuzzy_Rule_Learning.Shared.Fuzzy.Fuzzy
      • keel.Algorithms.Fuzzy_Rule_Learning.Shared.Fuzzy.FuzzyInterval

  • public class FuzzyInterval
extends Fuzzy

    Represents an interval fuzzy set. Each member of a interval fuzzy set has membership value of 1.0.
